<div id="hero-holder" class="main-slider-holder swiper-container main-slider-container propose-slider hero">
  <div class="swiper-wrapper">

    <% @pilots_page.sliders.each do |slider| -%>
      <div class="<%= slider.class_name %> swiper-slide" style="<%= slider.style %>">
        <div class="fade"></div>
        <div class="propose-slide">
          <div class="slide-content">
            <span class="typed small">Pilots</span>
            <span class="typed"><%= slider.formatted_title %></span>
            <p><%= slider.caption %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end -%>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="propose-a-pilot-project">
  <div class="propose-container">

    <div class="propose-title">
      <%= title "Propose a pilot project" %>
    </div>

    <div class="propose-description">
      <p>Do you want to use WikiHouse to build your project?</p>
      <p>The first WikiHouse technology is now in Beta, but there is not yet an established supply chain to provide it.</p>
      <p>We are currently developing new web tools and growing a wider network of architects, manufacturers, builders, insurers and suppliers ready to help you realise your project. In the meantime, there are a number of pilots happening around the world, from tiny studios to homes to whole neighbourhoods. If you would like your project to be one of these pilots, please take 5 minutes to tell us about it.</p>
      <p>We will try to connect you with the support you need to make it happen.</p>
      <p><a style="color: white; text-decoration: underline" href="https://s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/wikihouse.cc/WHouse_Guide_1.0.pdf" target="_blank">Here is an introductory guide to using WikiHouse</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="propose-form">
      <%= render "propose_form" %>
    </div>

    <div class="thanks" id="thank-you">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Thank you.</h1>
